tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5 sung ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_21076\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-21076\" style=\"width: 2123px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-21076\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Sinh-vien-VNH-di-thuc-te.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2123\" height=\"937\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-21076\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sinh vi\u00ean Khoa Du l\u1ecbch &#8211; Ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110H Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 t\u00edch l\u0169y ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u0103n h\u00f3a &#8211; l\u1ecbch s\u1eed &#8211; con ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>Th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u00f4n v\u00e0 thi ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng:<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Sinh vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Cao \u0111\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn vi\u00ean du l\u1ecbch c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1ebb h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn du l\u1ecbch m\u1edbi.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><b>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c thi <\/b>g\u1ed3m hai ph\u1ea7n L\u00fd thuy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 170 ph\u00fat.<\/p>\n<p><b>Th\u1eddi gian:<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd: \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y <b>25\/12\/2024 <\/b><b>&#8211;<\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/forms.gle\/fB1stRfGwcYhDw4v8\"><b> Form \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd<\/b><\/a><\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Th\u1eddi gian \u00f4n t\u1eadp: ng\u00e0y <b>26 